FBIS3-15053 "drsov041_b_94021" FBIS-SOV-94-041 Document Type:Daily Report 2 Mar 1994 RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS Political Issues Yeltsin Appoints Livshits To Head Team of Experts LD0203091694 Moscow Mayak Radio Network in Russian 0800 GMT 2 Mar 94 LD0203091694 Moscow Mayak Radio Network Language: Russian Article Type:BFN [Text] Boris Yeltsin issued an instruction today, appointing Aleksandr Yakovlevich Livshits head of the group of experts for the president of the Russian Federation. The same documents instruct Livshits to draft and submit to the president within one month a new statute on the group of experts. This was announced today by the press service of the head of state.
